        <div class="c-byline">

<div class="c-byline__author">
<div class="author-avatar"><img alt="Eleisha Foon" class="profile-thumb" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20240126025704im_/https://media.rnztools.nz/rnz/image/upload/s--ee3ekNnt--/ar_1:1,c_fill,f_auto,g_auto,q_auto,w_144/v1702412293/4KY2NLO_Tezza_4606_jpeg"/></div><div class="author-detail">
<span class="author-name"><a href="/web/20240126025704/https://www.rnz.co.nz/authors/eleisha-foon">Eleisha Foon</a></span>, <span class="author-job">RNZ Pacific Journalist</span>
<div class="author-social">
<span class="author-twitter icon-twitter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20240126025704/https://twitter.com/@eleishafoon ">@eleishafoon </a></span>
</div>
</div>
